        <item>
            <title>少年 JUMP 玩具展登陸銅鑼灣，打卡位 + 會場限定品</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/09/13/jump2024/life-tech/%e7%8e%a9%e5%85%b7/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=jump2024</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/09/13/jump2024/life-tech/%e7%8e%a9%e5%85%b7/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[arthur]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 13 Sep 2024 10:28:54 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[玩具]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1262814</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>銅鑼灣時代廣場於 2024 年 9 月 13 日正式展開全港首個「JUMP FIGURE CRAFT STUDIO」期間限定展覽，展期將持續至 11 月 3 日。這次展覽展示了《週刊少年 JUMP》四大經典作品，包括《龍珠》、《火影忍者》、《ONE PIECE》和《SPY×FAMILY 間諜家家酒》，並將漫畫角色以 Figure 形式呈現，讓參觀者從中回顧角色的演變和招式特色。展區內設置了多個場景，讓動漫迷可以深入瞭解角色的背景及故事發展。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1262862" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1215-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1215-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1215.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>《龍珠》展區重現了基洛博士的秘密實驗室，觀眾可以進入膠囊，化身成為人造人拍照留念。展區中展示了多款《龍珠》系列的珍貴 Figure，展現主角孫悟空及其他歷代角色的變化，從最早的造型到近期的形象演變，這些 Figure 不僅展現了角色的招式動作，也透過細膩的雕工展示出其鮮明的個性。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1262864" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1217-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1217-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1217.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1262865" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1218-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1218-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1218.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>在《ONE PIECE》展區，參觀者可以乘坐千陽號，透過多個展示的 Figure 瞭解不同版本的角色造型及發展過程。展區中特別展示了《ONE PIECE》系列 Figure 的材質和細節演變，從初代作品到當今的作品，Figure 的精緻度和動感都得到了顯著提升，帶領觀眾一同見證角色在動畫和漫畫中的成長。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1262866" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1210-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1210-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1210.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1262868" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1212-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1212-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1212.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1262869" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1213-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1213-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1213.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>《火影忍者》展區則重現了木葉忍者村的標誌大門，吸引了大量《火影忍者》粉絲前來打卡。展區內最大的亮點是 3.9 米高的火影巖 3D 場景以及 1 比 1 大小的漩渦鳴人立像，這些精美的展品為觀眾呈現了角色的標誌性招式，包括螺旋丸、仙法熔遁螺旋手裏劍等經典場景，並讓粉絲們可以近距離感受鳴人等角色的招式魅力。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1262871" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1207-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1207-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1207.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1262873" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1209-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1209-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1209.jpg 675w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1262876" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1210-1-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1210-1-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1210-1.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1262877" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1202-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1202-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1202.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>《SPY×FAMILY 間諜家家酒》展區以東國市鎮的大街為主題，展出了安妮亞和她的父親洛伊德·佛傑的 1:1 立像，這也是洛伊德首次在香港亮相。展區內的設計讓參觀者猶如置身於動畫中的場景，近距離觀察安妮亞一家在東國的生活情景。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1262880" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1204-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1204-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1204.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1262881" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1205-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1205-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1205.jpg 675w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></p><p>除了展覽部分，TAMASHII NATIONS POP-UP SPOT 快閃店同時在二樓中庭開設，發售超過 300 款商品，其中包括多款 JUMP 系列的獨家限定品。而５款會場限量商品將以網上登記抽籤的形式發售，粉絲們需透過 Tamashii Nations Hong Kong 的 Facebook 專頁查閲具體購買資訊，不過消息指現時已被全數認購售罄了。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1262883" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1255-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1255-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1255.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1262884" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1248-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1248-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1248.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1262885" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1250-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1250-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1250.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1262886" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1225-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1225-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1225.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1262887" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1230-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1