            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1262697</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">微信日前舉行發布會正式宣佈在微信支付、中國工商銀行（澳門）和澳門銀河的緊密合作下，將會在澳門銀河推出首個境外刷掌支付服務。本次合作項目首階段會在星際酒店、澳門銀河、澳門百老匯和銀河綜藝館共 60 多個商鋪和服務點率先引入刷掌登記及支付功能，已經開通內地微信錢包支付及刷掌支付的用户即可使用。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1262740" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/115screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/115screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/115screenshot.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1262739" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/029screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/029screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/029screenshot.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1262700 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/unknown-694x440.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="440" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/unknown-694x440.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/unknown-scaled.jpeg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">圖片來源：<a href="https://www.tencent.com/index.php/zh-cn/articles/2201934.html">騰訊</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">微信支付硬件創新負責人夏凱在發布會現場介紹刷掌支付的技術原理，以「掌紋 + 掌靜脈」的識別技術實現無接觸且高準確度的支付體驗。目前刷掌支付在境內已經廣泛地應用在零售、餐飲、交通等場景，微信支付跨境業務港澳台區域負責人陳張維希望境外地區引入刷掌支付技術能有效幫助境外商家提升經營效率。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_23582"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/yCY1MemXzuY?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p style="font-weight: 400;">目前澳門銀河亦就微信刷掌支付的引入而推出了一系列的優惠，中國內地微信支付用户在 9 月 10 日至 10 月 31 日活動期間於銀河娛樂集團成員旗下指定商户新開通及使用微信刷掌支付，首單消費可立即扣減高達 88.8 人民幣，於指定商户使用微信支付亦可享高達 180 人民幣的滿減券。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">資料來源：<a href="https://www.tencent.com/index.php/zh-cn/articles/2201934.html">騰訊</a>、<a href="https://www.galaxymacau.com/zh-hant/offers/dining/wave-and-pay/">澳門銀河</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">圖片來源：<a href="https://www.galaxymacau.com/zh-hant/offers/dining/wave-and-pay/">澳門銀河</a></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/09/03/apple-wechat-2/software/ios-app/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">傳微信拒絕支援 iPhone 16   Apple：正與騰訊協商解決</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/23/smartone-macau-service-ended/mobile-phone/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">數碼通停止澳門流動通訊服務，現有客户將轉至澳門電訊</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/05/govt-whatsapp-new-rule/software/pc-app/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">新指引限制公務員使用個人通訊軟件　需要獲部門主管批准才能用 WhatsApp</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/09/13/wechat-palmpayment-available-in-macau/life-tech/epayment/">微信刷掌支付登陸澳門，境外首站支援 + 用掌紋掌靜脈辨識技術</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
